          "description": "The muddy riverbank seems to be the least of your worries, as you start to remember how you ended up here, the familiar murmur seems to get louder here. The path to the north has been blocked by debris from the explosion, so it seems your only option is to venture along the muddy riverbank toward the murmurs. As you proceed south, you realize you've made a novice mistake and sprung a trap! You are whisked south by a mudslide; backtracking is out of the question.",
